        // They are within [MinX, MaxX], but actually all masked values
        // are exactly the multiples of Step starting at CMasked.
        // For the union to be contiguous [0, NewCX), we need:
        // CX >= MinX (range touches or overlaps masked region)
        // Actually, we just check if CX > MinX (overlap) or CX == MinX (adjacent)
